      • compareCalendarEntries

        public void compareCalendarEntries(java.util.ArrayList<LotusNotesCalendarEntry> lotusCalEntries,
                                   java.util.ArrayList<com.google.api.services.calendar.model.Event> googleCalEntries)
        Compare the Lotus and Google entries based on the Lotus modified timestamp and other items. On exit, lotusCalEntries will only contain the entries we want created and googleCalEntries will only contain the entries we want deleted.
